
Combine thinly sliced @red cabbage{300%g}, grated @carrots{150%g}, and diced @red onion{50%g}.

In a separate bowl, mix @mayonnaise{100%g}, @apple cider vinegar{30%ml}, @Dijon mustard{15%g}, @honey{15%g}, @salt{} to taste, and @black pepper{}.

Pour the dressing over the cabbage mixture, toss until well coated.

Refrigerate for ~{1%hour} before serving.

